---

---

<section id="about" class="section-container">
  <h2 class="section-title">
    <span class="text-gradient">About</span>
  </h2>

  <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-5">
    <div class="lg:col-span-3">
      <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
        I build backend systems, mostly in .NET and Go. I've worked on APIs, data pipelines,
        event-driven services, and the infrastructure that keeps them running. I care about things
        that matter in production — queries that don't time out, data that stays consistent, and
        services that degrade gracefully instead of falling over.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
        I'm comfortable across the stack from database design to deployment. Most of my professional
        experience is in the .NET ecosystem, but I reach for Go or Python when the problem calls for
        it.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
        Outside of coding, I contribute to open-source projects when I can and spend too much time
        tinkering with my homelab.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-2">
      <div class="card space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Quick Facts</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-400">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span
              class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-400"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-4 w-4"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              >
                <path
                  d="M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0"
                ></path>
                <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle>
              </svg>
            </span>
            Based in Vietnam
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span
              class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-400"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-4 w-4"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              >
                <path d="M16 20V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"></path>
                <path d="M2 9v11a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9"></path>
                <path d="M2 9h20"></path>
                <path d="M2 9l9.687 5.284a1 1 0 0 0 .626 0L22 9"></path>
              </svg>
            </span>
            Backend Engineering
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span
              class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-400"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-4 w-4"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              >
                <path
                  d="M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </span>
            .NET, C#, Go, Python
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span
              class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-400"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-4 w-4"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              >
                <rect width="20" height="8" x="2" y="2" rx="2"></rect>
                <rect width="20" height="8" x="2" y="14" rx="2"></rect>
                <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="6.01" y2="6"></line>
                <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="6.01" y2="18"></line>
              </svg>
            </span>
            PostgreSQL, Redis, RabbitMQ
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
